### ── apps/api/requests/wallets.http ──────────────────────────
### Run in SQLTools to find wallet IDs:
### SELECT id, owner_type, owner_id, balance, reserved_amount FROM wallets;
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api/v1
@token = <paste_your_access_token_here>
@walletId = <paste_wallet_id_here>

### Get wallet balance
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallets/{{walletId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get wallet transaction history (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallets/{{walletId}}/transactions?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get wallet history with date filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallets/{{walletId}}/transactions?from=2025-01-01&to=2025-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
